* Shadow Cat and Snow Tech walk towards the forest, hoping that the coverage 
would conceal them. Heading into the trees, they notice that all of the 
local wildlife was either gone or laying low. They both immedietly became 
nervous, as they new something was dreadfully wrong. Shadow Cat motioned to 
Snow Tech and they both pulled outtheir weapons, Shadow Cat her electrical 
blaster and Snow Tech his ice cannon. They walked silently and quickly, not 
desturbing anything with their passage.*

" Snow Tech, what do you think t......"

*Shadow Cat never got to finish her sentance, for out of a large stand of 
trees, the troop of alien droids burst out and began firing at them. Shadow 
Cat squeeled and ran, while Snow tech let loose a gasius rumble, and ran the 
opposite direction that Shadow Cat ran.*

Snow Tech: " EeeeeEeeeeEeeeeeeeeeEeeeeeEeeeeeeeee!"

* The bots immedietly split up into two groups and purseued after the 
fleeing bots. Shadow Cat burst from the bush, right into the middle of the 
battle field. She gave no thought but kept on running, kicking up dust and 
debrise as she ran. Meanwhile, Snow Tech was running out of the bush, near 
were Iron Raptor had given her orders. He burst from the bush in a cloud of 
leaves and twigs, feet going full speed. He ran into the feild, hoping that 
the other bots would confuse the aliens.
The Aliens on the other hand, smashed the surrounding trees to oblivion, 
making two large openings in the tree line. They entered the feild, and 
looked around, confused, where where the bots?....*
